**BitBooks.co** is a Bitcoin-only eBook marketplace allowing authors to list their book at commission and sell directly to the public.

##Listings
Listings are free. Payments can only be made in Bitcoin via direct pay or using [[BitPay]].

##Fees
Authors pay commission on sales, which is deducted by BitBooks before paying royalties. At time of writing the commission listed is 10% of sale price.

##Restrictions
There are few restrictions on content, but E-books must be original work and be listed by the copyright owner.  

##History

Launched in Spring 2013.

